title.narrative: COVID response - SP

description.narrative: With UNICEF technical support, the government was able to expand its cash assistance program to reach to over 165,000 households mostly affected by COVID-19 pandemic with monthly cash assistance.UNICEF was able to enhance access to education for over 24,000 children, through the provision of tablets with internet connections and pre-installed application to enable a safe learning experience. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:15/01/2022
